https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bombay-MAccabees@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bombay-MAccabees@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Bombay-MAccabees@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bombay-bicycle-club">孟买自行车俱乐部 (Bombay Bicycle Club)</a>回顾了他们参加 2010 年 NME 颁奖典礼的时光，即将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-maccabees">The Maccabees</a>合作。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/photos/history-of-the-nme-awards-tour-1406271">NME 颁奖典礼的历史</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>这篇文章是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/orlando-weeks">奥兰多威克斯</a>和同事发布的。本周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-maccabees-announce-huge-reunion-show-for-all-point-east-2025-buy-tickets-3806881">确认了他们复出的消息</a>，并宣布将于8月24日在首都维多利亚公园登台，这是他们八年来的首次合作演出。</p><p>这场演出恰逢他们的第四张也是最后一张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/the-maccabees-track-by-track-guide-to-their-fearless-new-album-marks-to-prove-it-762993">“Marks To Prove It”</a>发行十周年。</p><p>随后透露，The Maccabees 将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/all-points-east">All Points East</a>合作策划当天的完整阵容，其中包括“他们喜爱的新老艺术家”。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-maccabees-reveal-support-acts-for-all-points-east-2025-reunion-3807780">第一波开幕艺术家很快就被共享</a>，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bombay-bicycle-club">Bombay Bicycle Club</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-cribs">The Cribs</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dry-cleaning">Dry Cleaning</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nilufer-yanya">Nilüfer Yanya</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-murder-capital">The Murder Capital</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/divorce-announce-debut-album-drive-to-goldenhammer-with-insert-word-phrase-here-new-single-all-my-freaks-use-this-headline-nme-radar-3796610">Divorce</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prima-queen">Prima Queen</a> 。</p><p>现在，根据这一消息，孟买自行车俱乐部回顾了他们与 The Maccabees 一起在 2010 年 NME 颁奖典礼上表演的时光。</p><p>乐队在 Instagram 上分享了一篇新帖子，上传了两张图片：第一张是 All Points East 的新海报，第二张是 2010 年 NME 颁奖典礼的海报。</p><p> “我们不打算在明年夏天参加任何音乐节，但我们不能拒绝与老朋友重聚，”标题写道：“我们将在明年的 @allpointseastuk 上加入@themaccabees，距离我们第一次举办 15 年后在 NME 巡演中一起分享舞台。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBvoGM0INx0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,6